serviceLevel.descriptionDetail:
We will be waiting for you outside the airport where we will take you and other passengers to your respective hotels. Maximum 4 stops per shuttle. Please note that the shuttle only operates between 7:00 am and 6:00 pm. If you are not able to book our shared transportation please select a Private or Deluxe Transfer.

 

What You Need to Know
All airport transfers are door to door.
There are no hidden extras or local charges.
When you book on line you will receive an instant confirmation & boarding pass, specifying all the reservation details.
Vehicle type will depend on availability and number of passengers.


Arrivals & Departures
Your driver will be waiting for you outside the airport upon arrival. Please look for the Amstar logo on exiting the terminal. Our standard procedure is to monitor your flight arrival information and adjust your pick up time accordingly in the event of a delay.
Your driver will pick you up from the lobby of your hotel at the proposed pick-up time on the day of your departure. Our customer care representatives are on standby 24 hours a day in case of any last minute changes.
